column5: Husband just came home and said radio announced the Tournament has been canceled to the thousands that come in, there may be ice but not solid enough to hold the many people, cars and such to support all of them. I will try to find some more information as soon as possible.  Lorissa  Here is the information, just go to this website....  http://www.originalicefishingcontest.com/ontario.htm   Lorissa
